pid":"a686fe3e8d6b95070ec2f3094cb3cb216691c44e","tid":184861,"uid":23587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T06:01:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5937b57d1f2b2c66f763c45618e17e5961291e31","tid":184861,"uid":10035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T09:25:57.000Z","msg":"點解要經呢個平台？"},{"pid":"10f57b476b0d12e6e3689717ff7f4df89c84e2fe","tid":184861,"uid":15592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T09:31:05.000Z","msg":"不了, 個網頁版面有D柒"},{"pid":"2bb2e53c1037fd3e0f33b98b04d32b5acc9b331a","tid":184861,"uid":35780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T10:07:57.000Z","msg":"又叫人無私免費分享? <br />\n不了"},{"pid":"80864925bba1c11808c4e8ea0d9243b13a8d123a","tid":184861,"uid":23587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T13:13:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要經呢個平台？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似IG咁, <br />\n只係想多一個平台比人睇下自已既作品，<br />\n最終目的都係想宣傳。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你用相加IG 咪有人見到鐘意就會FOLLOW你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身 個平台最主要 係想比啲平時係香港既創作人,<br />\n唔洗比錢 都有個均等既機會去比其他人見到。<br />\n唔似YOUTUBE 咁要比錢BOOSTUP上黎。<br />\n無論新舊 出名唔出名 都係 同一待遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494a2de5b649a83875563b64dd4f3bf4cce6bf06","tid":184861,"uid":23587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T13:13:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不了, 個網頁版面有D柒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果有咩建議可以話我知 我執靚啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb343788401005bb7e24465237bdb46fccd9c9e8","tid":184861,"uid":23587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T13:17:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又叫人無私免費分享? <br />\n不了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係無私分享 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但請隨意加水印, 最好有IG 就比人知點去搵到更多你既作品 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個網站 唔係為左賺廣告費咩咩咩,<br />\n就係為左比人去分享自己 亦 僅僅係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以 如果覺得 我會攞左啲相去做私事,<br />\n就請加水印先比我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果都係唔想 都多謝你幫推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab31a96455aa0770131b60d00ddcff4f422529b","tid":184861,"uid":8318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T13:19:38.000Z","msg":"唔好用wix啦，你話你唔識寫code咪用wordpress<br />\n2017年了，網頁唔可以咁柒，你呢個真心唔掂"},{"pid":"057a66e0746c38ded70462e33093987d2e254b3d","tid":184861,"uid":23587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T13:50:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好用wix啦，你話你唔識寫code咪用wordpress<br />\n2017年了，網頁唔可以咁柒，你呢個真心唔掂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收到巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nWordpress, 我摸左陣, 比較似個BLOG<br />\n功能上就未必 可以 覆蓋得咁廣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都多謝你既提議 會盡我所能執好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他頁是咪都係麻麻地?<br />\n另外你係用 電話定電腦睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e8dca0413668509750d6e99fa838e7f60e825d","tid":184861,"uid":1123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T17:28:59.000Z","msg":"望到真係唔開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3da17a0b58c0167ae7fdc3a8cc85e4fbcc584a0","tid":184861,"uid":23587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:59:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>望到真係唔開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote